- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on sentence simplification.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a neural generation model for sentence simplification.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the proposed model is based on neural networks and involves training on large datasets.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the proposed model is a neural network-based model.
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves processing and generating language, which can be considered a form of sound.
